== Data Transfer Overview

Data transfers between parties will follow a defined schedule and process, using secure SFTP locations and clear notification procedures. All data is considered sensitive due to the inclusion of PHI and PII.

- *Delivery Schedule:* Data is delivered annually, with an estimated delivery in October of each year.

- *SFTP Locations:*
  - _Ongoing:_ Method under discussion. Host: TBD #h(1em) Path: TBD
  - _Historical:_ UH provides tab-delimited historical files. Optum retrieves these from UH's SFTP server. Host: `submit.phidc.org` #h(1em) Path: `/DATA/Actuarial Risk Scores/`

- *File Notifications:* Milliman emails Optum when annual files are delivered. Notices are sent to `hap_edw_inbound@optum.com` and Optum's distribution list. Optum will update Milliman if recipient addresses change.
